              %p
                I like the individual attention that I receive at Total Rehab.
                I like the atmosphere here, comfortable, clean, nice, friendly and relaxing.
                I feel the staff is extremely encouraging, caring, and well educated.
                I know the ethics of this facility and ownership is very high.
                I feel their concern/actions are always in my best interest.
            .author
